title: Are you still there?
description: The host considers that you are occupying a seat of the fishbowl without participating.
firstReason: If you just want to listen to the conversation, there's no need to occupy a seat of the fishbowl.
secondReason: If you are here due to technical problems, remember that you have to give access to microphone permissions so that the rest of the participants can hear you.
backButton: Got it, I want to go back to the room
